name: 6 Kings- King Mugi
description:
A wise man.
Eyes that glisten like the diamonds of Sierra Leone.
He has no time for idol chatter.
When he speaks it is for necessity only.
The elders come to him for reassurance.
The young come to him for advice.
Cattle flock at the scent of his approach.
Evil spirits scatter at the hint of his name.
Strength and knowledge personified.
All those near and far only quietly whisper his name. 
He hears them. He sees them. He knows them.
